{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"order","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/order","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>« <a href=\"/en-US/SVG/Attribute\" title=\"en/SVG/Attribute\">SVG Attribute reference home</a></p>\n\n<p>order 属性确定被用作<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/feConvolveMatrix\"><code>&lt;feConvolveMatrix&gt;</code></a>元素的矩阵的大小。</p>\n\n<p>提供的值必须是大于 0 的<a href=\"/en-US/SVG/Content_type#integer\" title=\"/en/SVG/Content_type#Integer\">&lt;整数&gt;</a>. 第一个值&lt;orderX&gt;,确定矩阵的列数。第二个值&lt;orderY&gt;确定矩阵的行数。如果&lt;orderY&gt;没有指定，那么它的默认值相当于&lt;orderX&gt;的值。</p>\n\n<p>一个典型的值是 order=\"3\". 建议只使用较小的值 (例如 3); 大值可能会导致较高的 CPU 开销而且通常界面上并不能表现出高耗能造成的效果。</p>\n\n<p>如果未指定该属性，则其效果就如同指定值为 3.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"usage_context","title":"Usage context","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">Categories</th>\n   <td>None</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">Value</th>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/SVG/Content_type#number-optional-number\" title=\"en/SVG/Content_type#Color\">&lt;number-optional-number&gt;</a></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">Animatable</th>\n   <td>Yes</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">Normative document</th>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/SVG11/filters.html#feConvolveMatrixElementOrderAttribute\" rel=\"external noopener\" class=\"external\">SVG 1.1 (2nd Edition)</a></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"example","title":"Example","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"elements","title":"Elements","isH3":false,"content":"<p>下列元素可以使用 order 属性</p>\n\n<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/feConvolveMatrix\"><code>&lt;feConvolveMatrix&gt;</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Usage context","id":"usage_context"},{"text":"Example","id":"example"},{"text":"Elements","id":"elements"}],"summary":"« SVG Attribute reference home","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"order","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/svg/attribute/order","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/svg/attribute/order/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG","title":"SVG"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute","title":"SVG 属性参考"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/order","title":"order"}],"pageTitle":"order - SVG | MDN","noIndexing":false}}